finish_timestamp = $$CurrentTimeStamp,
updated_at = $$CurrentTimeStamp
WHERE data_flow_name = 'DF_LOAD_dim_partner_V3_ODS' AND status= 'RUNNING';

SELECT 
	SRC_dim_lab.lab_id AS LAB_ID,
	coalesce(REPLACE(REPLACE(SRC_dim_lab.lab_name,char(10),char(05)),char(13),char(06)),'') AS LAB_NAME,
	coalesce(REPLACE(REPLACE(SRC_dim_lab.lab_code_name,char(10),char(05)),char(13),char(06)),'') AS LAB_CODE_NAME,
	coalesce(REPLACE(REPLACE(SRC_dim_lab.director,char(10),char(05)),char(13),char(06)),'') AS DIRECTOR,
	coalesce(REPLACE(REPLACE(SRC_dim_lab.lab_phone,char(10),char(05)),char(13),char(06)),'') AS LAB_PHONE,
	coalesce(REPLACE(REPLACE(SRC_dim_lab.shipping_address_city,char(10),char(05)),char(13),char(06)),'') AS SHIPPING_ADDRESS_CITY,
	coalesce(REPLACE(REPLACE(SRC_dim_lab.shipping_address_state,char(10),char(05)),char(13),char(06)),'') AS SHIPPING_ADDRESS_STATE,
	coalesce(REPLACE(REPLACE(SRC_dim_lab.shipping_address_country,char(10),char(05)),char(13),char(06)),'') AS SHIPPING_ADDRESS_COUNTRY,
	coalesce(REPLACE(REPLACE(cast('V3' as char(2)),char(10),char(05)),char(13),char(06)),'') AS SOURCE_SYSTEM,
	coalesce(REPLACE(REPLACE(CASE WHEN SRC_dim_lab.shipping_address_encrypted_street  IS NULL THEN NULL WHEN ((CONVERT(cast(AES_decrypt(unhex(SRC_dim_lab.shipping_address_encrypted_street ), unhex($PP_V3_ODS_DECRYPT_KEY)) AS CHAR) USING ascii) = cast(AES_decrypt(unhex(SRC_dim_lab.shipping_address_encrypted_street ), unhex($PP_V3_ODS_DECRYPT_KEY)) AS CHAR))) THEN CONVERT(cast(AES_decrypt(unhex(SRC_dim_lab.shipping_address_encrypted_street ), unhex($PP_V3_ODS_DECRYPT_KEY)) AS CHAR) USING ascii) ELSE 'Contains Invalid Characters'END,char(10),char(05)),char(13),char(06)),'') AS V_SHIPPING_ADDRESS_STREET,
	coalesce(REPLACE(REPLACE(CASE WHEN SRC_dim_lab.shipping_address_encrypted_suite  IS NULL THEN NULL WHEN ((CONVERT(cast(AES_decrypt(unhex(SRC_dim_lab.shipping_address_encrypted_suite ), unhex($PP_V3_ODS_DECRYPT_KEY)) AS CHAR) USING ascii) = cast(AES_decrypt(unhex(SRC_dim_lab.shipping_address_encrypted_suite ), unhex($PP_V3_ODS_DECRYPT_KEY)) AS CHAR))) THEN CONVERT(cast(AES_decrypt(unhex(SRC_dim_lab.shipping_address_encrypted_suite ), unhex($PP_V3_ODS_DECRYPT_KEY)) AS CHAR) USING ascii) ELSE 'Contains Invalid Characters'END,char(10),char(05)),char(13),char(06)),'') AS V_SHIPPING_ADDRESS_SUITE,
	coalesce(REPLACE(REPLACE(
case when SRC_dim_lab.shipping_address_zip4 is null then SRC_dim_lab.shipping_address_zip5 
else concat(SRC_dim_lab.shipping_address_zip5 ,'-',SRC_dim_lab.shipping_address_zip4 )
end

,char(10),char(05)),char(13),char(06)),'') AS V_SHIPPING_ADDRESS_POSTALCODE,
	coalesce(REPLACE(REPLACE(cast('SHIPPING' as char(20)),char(10),char(05)),char(13),char(06)),'') AS V_ADDRESS_TYPE
 FROM $DO_GHL1_MY_MYSQL_DIM_LAB SRC_dim_lab

WITH  EXPR_NAME 
 AS 
( 
SELECT 
	SRC_dim_lab.LAB_ID AS LAB_ID
	,SRC_dim_lab.LAB_NAME AS LAB_NAME
	,SRC_dim_lab.LAB_CODE_NAME AS LAB_CODE_NAME
	,SRC_dim_lab.DIRECTOR AS DIRECTOR
	,SRC_dim_lab.LAB_PHONE AS LAB_PHONE
	,SRC_dim_lab.SHIPPING_ADDRESS_CITY AS SHIPPING_ADDRESS_CITY
	,SRC_dim_lab.SHIPPING_ADDRESS_STATE AS SHIPPING_ADDRESS_STATE
	,SRC_dim_lab.SHIPPING_ADDRESS_COUNTRY AS SHIPPING_ADDRESS_COUNTRY
	,SRC_dim_lab.SOURCE_SYSTEM AS SOURCE_SYSTEM
	,SRC_dim_lab.V_SHIPPING_ADDRESS_STREET AS V_SHIPPING_ADDRESS_STREET
	,SRC_dim_lab.V_SHIPPING_ADDRESS_SUITE AS V_SHIPPING_ADDRESS_SUITE
	,SRC_dim_lab.V_SHIPPING_ADDRESS_POSTALCODE AS V_SHIPPING_ADDRESS_POSTALCODE
	,SRC_dim_lab.V_ADDRESS_TYPE AS V_ADDRESS_TYPE
	,CURRENT_TIMESTAMP AS CURRENT_AT
	,CURRENT_TIMESTAMP AS UPDATED_AT
	,0 AS IS_DELETED
	,$SP_MAX_KEY.max_key  + row_number() OVER (ORDER BY (select 1)) AS PARTNER_KEY
 FROM 
	$TFORM_SRC_dim_lab SRC_dim_lab
 )MERGE $DO_GHL1_MS_IDM_DIM_PARTNER TGT_dim_partner 
 USING EXPR_NAME EXPR_NAME 
  ON TGT_dim_partner.partner_pid = EXPR_NAME.LAB_ID AND 
TGT_dim_partner.source_system = EXPR_NAME.SOURCE_SYSTEM
 WHEN MATCHED THEN 
UPDATE SET
	partner_name = EXPR_NAME.LAB_NAME
	,partner_code = EXPR_NAME.LAB_CODE_NAME
	,address_type = EXPR_NAME.V_ADDRESS_TYPE
	,partner_address1 = EXPR_NAME.V_SHIPPING_ADDRESS_STREET
	,partner_address2 = EXPR_NAME.V_SHIPPING_ADDRESS_SUITE
	,partner_city = EXPR_NAME.SHIPPING_ADDRESS_CITY
	,partner_state = EXPR_NAME.SHIPPING_ADDRESS_STATE
	,partner_postal_code = EXPR_NAME.V_SHIPPING_ADDRESS_POSTALCODE
	,partner_country = EXPR_NAME.SHIPPING_ADDRESS_COUNTRY
	,contact_name = EXPR_NAME.DIRECTOR
	,contact_phone = EXPR_NAME.LAB_PHONE
	,updated_at = EXPR_NAME.UPDATED_AT
	,is_deleted = EXPR_NAME.IS_DELETED
 WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN 
INSERT
(partner_key,partner_pid,partner_name,partner_code,address_type,partner_address1,partner_address2,partner_city,partner_state,partner_postal_code,partner_country,contact_name,contact_phone,source_system,created_at,updated_at,is_deleted)
VALUES (
EXPR_NAME.PARTNER_KEY,
EXPR_NAME.LAB_ID,
EXPR_NAME.LAB_NAME,
EXPR_NAME.LAB_CODE_NAME,
EXPR_NAME.V_ADDRESS_TYPE,
EXPR_NAME.V_SHIPPING_ADDRESS_STREET,
EXPR_NAME.V_SHIPPING_ADDRESS_SUITE,
EXPR_NAME.SHIPPING_ADDRESS_CITY,
EXPR_NAME.SHIPPING_ADDRESS_STATE,
EXPR_NAME.V_SHIPPING_ADDRESS_POSTALCODE,
EXPR_NAME.SHIPPING_ADDRESS_COUNTRY,
EXPR_NAME.DIRECTOR,
EXPR_NAME.LAB_PHONE,
EXPR_NAME.SOURCE_SYSTEM,
EXPR_NAME.CURRENT_AT,
EXPR_NAME.UPDATED_AT,
EXPR_NAME.IS_DELETED)#SEMICOLON_DELIM#
